ActAssisted Human Reproduction Act
SubjectOrder Fixing (1) the First Anniversary of the Day on which this Order is Made as the Day on which Section 12 of that Act Comes into Force; and (2) the Day on which this Order is Made as the Day on which Sections 45 to 58 of that Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing (1) the first anniversary of the day on which this Order is made as the day on which section 12 of the ASSISTED HUMAN REPRODUCTION ACT, chapter 2 of the Statutes of Canada, 2004, COMES INTO FORCE; and (2) the day on which this Order is made as the day on which sections 45 to 58 of the ASSISTED HUMAN REPRODUCTION ACT, chapter 2 of the Statutes of Canada, 2004, COME INTO FORCE.
